Name: jut
About the game: A game about beach hunting Help a trash monster complete its checklist. Transport trash in your belly or on your head, and throw it away to make more items wash up. More things wash up while the game is closed. Find all the different items to complete the game! 15+ items to collect checklist to see what you collected wear a stack of trash hats ~20 minutes of play time (a couple of hours (over time) to find everything) Controls walk: move the mouse pick up: LMB and RMB explode: hold both LMB and RMB pause menu: escape Sokpop makes a new game every two weeks!
